## Tests

- **Unit** (`src/**/*.test.ts`, next to source) — mocked dependencies, no I/O
- **Integration** (`src/**/__integration__/*.int.test.ts`) — real DB via Testcontainers locally, GH Actions service containers in CI. Never mock the DB here.

Integration test helpers:
- `__integration__/helpers/http.ts` — `api()` and `authedApi(role)` — pre-configured supertest agents
- `__integration__/helpers/db.ts` — `resetDb()` runs in `beforeEach`
- `__integration__/helpers/global-setup.ts` — boots the DB container once per suite

## Hard rules

- Never `console.log` — use the structured logger
- Never touch the DB driver outside `repository.ts`
- Never `throw new Error(...)` from a request path — use `ApiError`
- Never serialize Mongo `_id` directly — call `toWire(doc)` first
- Never let an `ApiError` leak with a 5xx that should be a 4xx — pick the right status
- Never log secrets, JWTs, or full request bodies — pino redaction handles common cases; check on a new field
